result.name: KK Curry Kebabs

reviews.text: I had chicken curry and Naan, it's costly as per the taste, quantity and quality they provide. Minimum you have to spend 100HKD per person if you are going in group.
This small shop has been here over ten years! Still my favourite curry place.

Actually we stayed in Hong-Kong for four days on some business work we use to go various Indian restaurants for lunch and dinner in the same way or fast KK Curry Kebabs came into the list, Hong Kong is expensive city when we compare other but in this restaurant they are charging like bomb price in spite of they are not giving good food also we ordered two roti, mutton curry, one chicken kebab and one mutton biryani no onions, no raita, no curry for Biryani when we asked reply was will be served on extra cost we agreed after this the bill amount was 356 Hong Kong $ is almost 19000 rupees but our stomach didn't even filled half the quantity was very less and taste also is below average felt very very bad.
Very nice

Traditional Indian restaurant, friendly shop with passion. Tried their lamb and chicken masala curry (medium spicy.. yeah the level of spicy can be chosen! ), roasted chicken, mango lassi, plain naan bread. Love them! Only one tiny flaw... rice, it's a little bit soft for me, maybe too much water added

result.name: 祖堯邨

reviews.text: 巴士上拍攝，不認識，冇意見！
老舊的房屋協會屋邨，依山而建，一層一層有特色，人情味濃 。
居住的環境比較清靜 可惜的是夜晚只有一間酒樓供晚飯 沒有快餐之類的食品可以選擇 成獨市生意
an estate, living place, nothing special

一個 面積 小小 同時 日子 比較老舊 的 屋邨，不過 保養得 很好 。
居民友善 親切 ☺
社區配套 整備 ， 街市 ，超市，便利店 ，社區中心， 酒樓 ， 食店 ，補習社 ，老人中心 ，牙齒保健 ，銀行 ，游泳池 ， 小學 及 中學 等等 想不到 的多 😁
屋邨 內 竟然 擁有 一個 小小的 巴士總站 (單一條行線)，小巴中途站 ，遠了點的 荔景 港鐵站 ， 交通 也 算是 方便 。
很多 節日 ，中央廣場 地區 也有 不小 志願團體 為 居民舉辦活動 ，比如 有聲有色 的 演唱晚會 及 熱熱鬧鬧 的 攤位遊戲 也為 居民帶來 無限 的 歡樂 及 溫暖 😄
現在 屋邨 應該 是 第三代 居民 成長 的 時間 ，小孩子 多了 ， 爺爺嫲嫲 當然也多了 。三代同堂 的 溫馨日子 希望 可以 不斷 延續下去 。

result.name: KK正宗印度餐廳

reviews.text: 味道是正正宗宗印度架哩，好好食好香好味😋可惜埋單錢包會輕了不少的。
質數一流，價錢平，但對比街外印度餐廳食物選擇少，老闆印度人非常有善！值得加分^^
一個字, 中伏! 荔景屋村商場舖，裝修簡陋, 中環高級餐廳收費!! 二件咖哩牛 白飯 一罐汽水 收$128大元! 散叫咖哩羊 得三四件 收$88大元! 痴L線咩
I had chicken curry and Naan, it's costly as per the taste, quantity and quality they provide. Minimum you have to spend 100HKD per person if you are going in group.
東西很難吃！😨
